<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ğŸ§ª Test Final - Fire Salamander CorrigÃ©</title>
    <style>
